PREREQUISITES:
- A running web server with PHP5+
- Access to a MySQL server

SUCCESSFULLY TESTED IN:
- IE9+
- Firefox 4+
- Chrome 8+
- May work in other HTML5 capable browsers

SETUP:
- Copy all project files to your webserver
- Setup a new database on your MySQL server for the games data.
- From within your new MySQL database, run the SQL-scripts in /src/database (starting with the earliest), then run /srv/database/levels/levels.sql to import levels and level data.
- Change the content of /settings.empty.php to match your MySQL server settings and rename the file to /settings.php
- The game is now fully set up and can be access by pointing your browser to your webserver.
